cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

This paper is about improving stability and providing probabilistic performance guarantees in off-policy actor-critic deep reinforcement learning regimes. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.CV, in that order.
